  "title": "Nether Wart Blocks to Nether Warts",
  "description": "A configurable mod that lets you craft Nether Wart Blocks back to Nether Warts",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/wishful-recipes\"><img src=\"https://images2.imgbox.com/91/a0/caG03Acz_o.png\" alt=\"This mod has been made part of Wishful Recipes. Please check it out by clicking on this. It can dynamically generate recipes on its own, meaning it is highly compatible with other mods and requires less configuration. \"/></a>\n<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q12CmpU.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/mars_\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/ko--fi-donate-FF5E5B?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=ko-fi&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on ko-fi\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/nether-wart-block-to-nether-warts\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/517690?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/nether-wart-block-to-nether-warts\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/nether-wart-block-to-nether-warts?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This Minecraft mod allows you to craft a configurable number of Nether Warts from a Nether Wart Block, making it much easier to store and farm Nether Warts.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8XbNbev.png\"/></p></center>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Configuration</strong></summary>\n<p>You can configure this mod directly in-game or edit the JSON file <code>config/netherwartblock.json</code> in your profile folder. Please note that any changes will require restarting Minecraft to take effect.</p>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>wartAmount</b> - determines how many Nether Warts you get</p>\n</details>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://url-shortener.curseforge.com/rmnuC\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/y3LiTfU.png\"/></a></p>\n",
